---
import WhatsAppButton from './ui/WhatsAppButton.astro';
---

<section class="relative py-20 md:py-28 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background effects -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[150px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-secondary/8 rounded-full blur-[80px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 text-center" data-reveal>
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-8">
      <span class="text-primary text-xs font-medium">Atendimento personalizado</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-tight text-balance">
      Cuide da sua saúde<br />
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-primary-light to-secondary">hoje mesmo</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="text-text-muted text-lg mt-6 max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Escolha simples, sem complicação. Fale com a gente pelo WhatsApp e descubra os melhores produtos naturais para você.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-10">
      <WhatsAppButton
        text="Comprar agora"
        message="Olá! Quero conhecer os produtos naturais do Empório Vida Leve."
        class="text-lg px-10 py-4 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(59,175,59,0.2)]"
      />
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-muted text-sm">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        Resposta rápida garantida
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
